reviewText: Hilarious short documentary which shows a Cambodian youth listening to rock music for the first time! Other short movies are cool too.  (from the Florida Film Festival program guide) "A Taiwanese rock and roll guru teaches a Cambodian Youth Vuth about Motorhead, the Ramones, the Kinks, Led Zeppelin, and more in this provocative cross-cultural documentary." Watch as Vuth hears the Kinks, the Ramones, the Doors, AC/DC and Motorhead for the first time in this strikingly unique Asian rockumentary!
